kukṣau kukṣisthajantau ca" iti yādavaḥ || tasyādhānam utpādanaṃ tad eva kṣaṇa utsavaḥ | sukhahetutvād iti bhāvaḥ || "nirvyāpārasthitau kālaviśeṣotsavayoḥ kṣaṇaḥ" ity amaraḥ || tasmin paricayād abhyāsād dhetoḥ khe vyomni | ābaddhamālāḥ || garbhādhānasukhārthaṃ tvatsamīpe baddhapaṅktaya ity arthaḥ || uktaṃ ca karṇodaye-"garbhaṃ balākā dadhate 'bhrayogān nāke nibaddhāvalayaḥ samantāt" iti || balākā balākāṅganā nayanasubhagaṃ dṛṣṭipriyaṃ bhavantaṃ nūnaṃ satyaṃ seviṣyante || anukūlamārutacātakaśabditabalākādarśanānāṃ śubhasūcakatvaṃ śakunaśāstre dṛṣṭaṃ tadvistarabhayān nālekhi ||

<commentary>na ca tasyā nāśādvrataskhalanādvā nirarthakastvatprayāsa ity āha-tāṃ ceti || he megha, divasānām avaśiṣṭadinānāṃ gaṇanāyāṃ saṅkhyāne tatparām āsaktām || "tatpare pratitāsaktau" ity amaraḥ || ata evāvyāpannām amṛtām | śāpāvasāne madāmanamatyāśayā jīvantīm ity arthaḥ | ekaḥ patir yasyāḥ saikapatnī tām | pativratām ity arthaḥ || "nityaṃ sapatnyādiṣu" iti ṅīp nakāraś ca || bhrātur me jāyāṃ bhrātṛjāyām | mātṛrvan niḥśaṅkadarśanīyām ity āśayaḥ | tāṃ matpriyām avihatagatir avicchinnagatiḥ sann avaśyaṃ drakṣyasi cālokayiṣyasa eva || tathā hi | āśātitṛṣṇā || "āśā digatitṛṣṇayoḥ" iti yādavaḥ || badhyate 'neneti bandho bandhanam | vṛntam iti yāvat | āśaiva bandha āśābandhaḥ kartā || praṇayi premayuktam ata eva kusumasadṛśam sukumāram ity arthaḥ | ata eva viprayoge virahe sadyaḥpāti sadyobhraṃśanaśīlam aṅganānāṃ hṛdayaṃ jīvitam || "hṛdayaṃ jīvite citte vakṣasyākūtayoḥ" iti śabdārṇave || prāyaśaḥ prāyeṇa ruṇaddhi pratibadhnāti || arthāntaranyāsaḥ ||</commentary>

saṃprati sahāyasampattiś cāstīty āha-kartum iti || yad garjitaṃ kartṛ mahīm ucchilandhrām udbhūtakandalikām |
